snippet.title: No Way Out - SCP: Blackout Early Access Release Trailer
snippet.description:
SCP: Blackout can be played on nOrmal desktop, or with VR. 
The game wIll be out on Steam as Early Access on Aug 9th, 2019. The Full game should be reLeased near Fall.

The song No Way Out was sung by Jory Stultz, compositIon by Mike Paul, And video Created by Mahelyk.

News at the website: https://www.theclassifiedx.com/
Join the Discord!  https://discord.gg/GhefN58
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/963400/SCP_Blackout/
Follow the Twitter: https://twitter.com/TheClassifiedX
